      • calendarSyncEnabled

        public Configuration.Builder calendarSyncEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Set whether or not calendar synchronization should be enabled.

        Note that for this feature to work, the client must have the Manifest.permission.READ_CALENDAR permission granted before calling InrixCore.initialize(Context, Configuration).

        Parameters:
        enabled - true if it should be enabled, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        Current instance.
        See Also:
        ItineraryManager.getItinerary(ItineraryManager.GetItineraryOptions, ItineraryManager.IGetItineraryResponseListener), CalendarTrip

        Current instance.

      • calendarDefaultNotificationTime

        public Configuration.Builder calendarDefaultNotificationTime(int notificationTimeMinutes)
        Set the default notification time for calendar events. This is the notification time (in minutes) before the departure time for the user to arrive on time for the start of the calendar event (including travel time).
        Parameters:
        notificationTimeMinutes - Notification time in minutes. Must be greater or equal 0 and less or equal 60.
        Returns:
        Current instance.
        See Also:
        Configuration.Builder.calendarNotificationsEnabled(boolean)

      • tripRecordingEnabled

        public Configuration.Builder tripRecordingEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Set whether or not trip recording should be enabled. This feature allows INRIX to learn the user's frequent trips and locations.
        Parameters:
        enabled - true if it should be enabled, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        Current instance.
        See Also:
        ItineraryManager.getItinerary(ItineraryManager.GetItineraryOptions, ItineraryManager.IGetItineraryResponseListener), LearnedTrip, LocationsManager.getLearnedLocations(LocationsManager.GetLearnedLocationsOptions, LocationsManager.IGetLearnedLocationsListener), LearnedLocation

      • locationLearningEnabled

        public Configuration.Builder locationLearningEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Sets a value that indicates whether location learning should be enabled. This feature is a lightweight version of Configuration.Builder.tripRecordingEnabled(boolean) that only learns frequent locations.
        Parameters:
        enabled - true if it should be enabled, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        Current instance.
        See Also:
